_sText:
This is an F-302 Starfighter  from Stargate.

I wont textured it wright, so if you want to it you can texture it for yourself. 

I build it after i had build the prefab of the BC-304 Daedalus (http://www.fpsbanana.com/prefabs/2791) to check of its size is ok.

So if yu use my Daedalus prefab you can put this Fighter into the hangar bays in the left and right wing.
